OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775981092
OL,3,CTV presenter Eamonn Holmes recovering
OL,4,Cin hospital after stroke
OL,6,FTV presenter Eamonn Holmes is
OL,7,Frecovering in hospital after a stroke,
OL,8,FGB News has said.
OL,10,FIn a statement on Saturday, a GB News
OL,11,Fspokesperson said Holmes, 66, "was
OL,12,Ftaken ill last week and it was later
OL,13,Fconfirmed he had suffered a stroke".
OL,15,F"He is currently responding well to
OL,16,Ftreatment," the spokesperson added.
OL,18,F"Eamonn has asked for privacy as he
OL,19,Ffocuses on getting better.
OL,26,@sD@_OUuD@cO]wD@AOUxD@KO]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
