PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775981092
OL,3,CTV presenter Eamonn Holmes recovering
OL,4,Cin hospital after stroke
OL,6,F"His colleagues and everyone at GB
OL,7,FNews wish him a speedy recovery and
OL,8,Flook forward to welcoming him back to
OL,9,Fthe people's channel when he is ready
OL,10,Fto return."
OL,12,FThe Northern Irish broadcaster
OL,13,Fpresents GB News Breakfast with his co-
OL,14,Fhost Ellie Costello.
OL,16,FAlex Armstrong will present in his
OL,17,Fabsence this week, the broadcaster
OL,18,Fadded.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@KO]
