PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775981092
OL,3,CTV presenter Eamonn Holmes recovering
OL,4,Cin hospital after stroke
OL,6,FAngelos Frangopoulos, chief executive
OL,7,Fof GB News, said: "Eamonn is a loved
OL,8,Fmember of the GB News family, and
OL,9,Fwe're with him every step of the way
OL,10,Fas he recovers."
OL,12,FHolmes has long battled issues after
OL,13,Fdislodging discs in his back which he
OL,14,Fsaid previously impinged on his
OL,15,Fsciatic nerve and affected the
OL,16,Fmobility of his right leg.
OL,18,FHe previously spoke about going
OL,19,Fthrough spinal surgery, a double hip
OL,20,Freplacement, and his struggles walking
OL,21,Fand using a mobility scooter.
OL,26,@oD@SOUrD@PO]
