OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775981092
OL,3,CTV presenter Eamonn Holmes recovering
OL,4,Cin hospital after stroke
OL,6,FHolmes had a couple of falls in May
OL,7,Flast year which seem to have taken
OL,8,Fplace only weeks apart.
OL,10,FThe former This Morning host was taken
OL,11,Fto hospital after a first fall at his
OL,12,Fhome, then fell from his chair live on-
OL,13,Fair.
OL,15,FDuring his GB News Breakfast show, a
OL,16,Fcrash could be heard while the camera
OL,17,Fwas focused on their guest,
OL,18,Fcommentator Charlie Rowley.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
