PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775981092
OL,3,CTV presenter Eamonn Holmes recovering
OL,4,Cin hospital after stroke
OL,6,FCo-host Ellie Costello could be heard
OL,7,Fsaying "oh my gosh" off-screen, and
OL,8,FHolmes pleaded with Rowley to "carry
OL,9,Fon" before the presenter returned to
OL,10,Fthe show following a break.
OL,12,FHolmes then said: "Welcome back. Good
OL,13,Fto see you again. Especially good for
OL,14,Fme to see you again. I am still alive,
OL,15,Fyes.
OL,26,@oD@HOUoD@SO]pD@_OUqD@CO]tD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
