PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775981092
OL,3,CTV presenter Eamonn Holmes recovering
OL,4,Cin hospital after stroke
OL,6,F"And they're very wonky wheels on
OL,7,Fchairs that we've got here, and matter
OL,8,Fof fact, we don't really like the
OL,9,Fchairs full stop, do we? They're a bit
OL,10,Fslippy and slidey and I've slipped and
OL,11,Fslid off mine there.
OL,13,F"Not the first guest to have done so,
OL,14,Fwe've had a few, they have to remain
OL,15,Fnameless because they're well known
OL,16,Fpeople, but they've hit the floor
OL,17,Freally badly, quite frightening.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775981092
OL,3,CTV presenter Eamonn Holmes recovering
OL,4,Cin hospital after stroke
OL,6,F"And it was a bit of a shock for me
OL,7,Fbecause I've had a fall in my bathroom
OL,8,Ftwo weeks ago, which hospitalised me,
OL,9,Fand that hit me again right in the
OL,10,Fback. (I'm) really, really sore.
OL,11,FReally sore."
OL,13,FHe later said the chair "gave way"
OL,14,Fwhich meant he was lying flat on his
OL,15,Fback.
OL,17,FHe added: "As the morning goes on, you
OL,18,Ffeel aches and pains.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@MO]uD@YOUuD@bO]yD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775981092
OL,3,CTV presenter Eamonn Holmes recovering
OL,4,Cin hospital after stroke
OL,6,F"The worst thing about this, of
OL,7,Fcourse, this was at a time when I was
OL,8,Fhospitalised two weeks ago for a very
OL,9,Fsimilar fall in the same area, back of
OL,10,Fthe head, my neck, my shoulders.
OL,12,F"So it all came back, as it were."
OL,14,FHolmes told The Sun newspaper in 2022
OL,15,Fthat his health problems caused issues
OL,16,Fin his marriage to Loose Women star
OL,17,FRuth Langsford.
OL,19,F"Even my own family are bored of my
OL,20,Fmoaning," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUtD@bO]{D@AOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
