PN,44709
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775981092
OL,3,CTV presenter Eamonn Holmes recovering
OL,4,Cin hospital after stroke
OL,6,F"It has caused some strain and Ruth is
OL,7,Ffed up of hearing about it and of me
OL,8,Fsaying I can't walk the dog or tidy
OL,9,Fup, but I can't help it. It's agony."
OL,11,FLangsford and Holmes announced their
OL,12,Fsplit in 2024, after tying the knot in
OL,13,F2010 following more than a decade
OL,14,Ftogether.
